"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/5/13398?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Chronic kidney disease (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?34/10/34977?source=see_link\">",
"      Patient information: Constipation in adults (Beyond the Basics)",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
