"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         2.5 mg/3 mL",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         5 mg/mL (0.5 percent)",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        0.63-2.5 mg in 3 cc of saline every 4-6 hours, as needed",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        1.25-5 mg in 3 cc of saline every 4-8 hours, as needed",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        May mix with cromolyn solution, budesonide inhalant suspension, or ipratropium solution for nebulization. May double dose for severe exacerbations.",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
