"         1.25 mg/0.5 mL",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         1.25 mg/3 mL",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        0.31-1.25 mg in 3 cc every 4-6 hours, as needed",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        0.31-0.63 mg, every 8 hours, as needed",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         Does not have FDA-approved labeling for children &lt;6 years of age.",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         The product is a sterile-filled preservative-free unit dose vial.",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         Compatible with budesonide inhalant suspension.",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
